          <Pad Id="AVfwIsZzS3zLaondTLLyPJ" Bounds="132,276,324,120" ShowValueBox="true" isIOBox="true" Value="The 'ColorMap' with the plain fallback color is used for the diffuse color of the Material. &#xD;&#xA;&#xD;&#xA;The 'Diffuse' feature works with colors or color textures, compare it to the Metalness or Roughness, which are just single values or grayscale textures.">
